    <h2 class="clearfix contentGroup cgMedium"><a href="/magazine" title="Magazine" class="cgLabel cgMagazine">Magazine</a></h2>   

    
        <h1>Exposed: Wikileaks&#39; secrets</h1>
    
    <div class="articleMeta clearfix">

            <div>By <a href="/search/author/Annabel+Symington" title="View all articles by Annabel Symington" class="fn">Annabel Symington</a></div>
        
        <div class="published">01 September 09</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix">
        
                <div class="imageWrapper">
                    <img alt="" src="http://cdni.wired.co.uk/620x258/w_z/wikileaks_article_620x258.jpg" class="landscape_2_40_620 image" />
                    
                </div>
                
        <div class="articleSidebar1">
            
    <div class="subscribe linkit">
        <img alt="" src="http://cdni.wired.co.uk/150x185/k_n/Magazine_6.jpg" class="portrait_1_23_185 linkme" />
        <p><a href="http://ad.doubleclick.net/clk;227508490;34725390;j" title="Subscribe to Wired magazine for only &#163;2 an issue" target="_blank">Subscribe to Wired magazine for only &#163;2 an issue</a></p>
    </div>

            
                    <div class="related linkList2">
